# UI Rules

- UI only orchestrates actions (import/export/generate docs) and displays status/errors/results.
- Keep business logic in shared/main modules, not inside UI components.
- Use typed message contracts from `src/shared/messaging/types.ts`.
- Keep controls explicit: no silent destructive actions without clear status feedback.
